  <description type="morphology">Plants annual, not rhizomatous, stoloniferous, or bulbiferous. Stems erect,
        branched, 1–10 cm. Leaves alternate, erect, not distinctly petiolate, with clasping leaf
        sheaths; blade linear, 5–50 × 0.5–2 mm. Inflorescences terminal, 1-bracteate; bract linear
        to oblanceolate, 1–6 mm. Flowers 4–12; sepals 1.5–2.5 mm; petals 5, white, 1.5–3 mm; stamens
        3, anther yellow. Seeds 0.8–1.2 mm, tuberculate; elaiosome absent. 2n = 14.</description>
